Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺振從頭再做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的劍道部好不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為換了個指導  練習超嚴格的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到去年為止都是個懶懶散散的部團呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連竹劍的打擊聲都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:19.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說一年級都不少人陸續退出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在搞那種熱血…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不時興了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！別停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大賽你初戰就輸掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人擊中面和腹部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說你為什麼輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方排名在我前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的運氣不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你有什麼地方不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中力不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及練習不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那就進行更多的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週不是還有練習賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級還只能練擺振
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？少了兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美和美砂怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們說太嚴格受不了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…一年級的退部了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想走的就讓她們走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年級剩下的女生就只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  小望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也退出好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是連你都走了  一年級不就只剩下我一個了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  東同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是…東同學吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小東東！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  我做了什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  我們走  小東東
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點快一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等等  你們給我說明一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是劍道部的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍道部…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小東東國中練過劍道吧？對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很強對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  加入劍道部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會加入劍道社的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  東
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為什麼為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其實不喜歡劍道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小就很喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…父母說上高中後就不能再練
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也這麼決定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  真的非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼啊  小東東？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好太可惜妖怪都要跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說  已經跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜啦！太可惜啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  就是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當參觀一下跟我們走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要讓她參觀一下部團活動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會想繼續練習下去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡  萬分榮幸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為什麼我要穿上防具…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說只參觀一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想回去的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須打倒我們兩個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然是出不去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就…奉陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同學  我去拿簸箕來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要下雨了  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  我今天沒帶傘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部室裡面有的  不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃前輩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是  那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面擊！好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好贊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  東
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:09:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好強呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東  你什麼時候開始練劍道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小學開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有經驗  技術也棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要…好想要但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思  耽擱你的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再耽誤你一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.74,0:10:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一場吧  東同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃亮～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰比較厲害啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是勇次君囉  他是男孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲  不要小看小東東哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  要知道我們是沒贏一局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不再趕回去念書的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊  小東東
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最後還是勇次連得兩分…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生對上勇次君打成那樣很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果再繼續下去的話  搞不好我會被拿下一分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我突然提出這樣的要求嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她是第五人的話我就放心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛！就是嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠色終於要定下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子就能正常地進行團體戰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不聽人說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東她是不會加入劍道社的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不會讓她加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說想讓她加入的人不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不甘心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是必須放棄啊！把東忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…她可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東的考試成績
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…確實很糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常認真  從沒有請假或者遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課也都認真聽講做筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…確實很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是不會念書  入學考試的時候也有像樣的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過不是迷糊到弄錯考試範圍  就是答題把答案寫錯行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續練劍道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績可能又要再掉一級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想要考上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師  請你不要強求她加入劍道部了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…她可是…沒辦法參加啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要更加努力念書  提高成績才行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很清楚  但只有放棄小東東囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人沒這個意思的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定不想再練劍道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用竹劍與她交流過  所以很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東她非常喜歡劍道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身體內有著火熱的劍道之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她絕對會以劍士的身份回到這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課本和練習冊都忘帶回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫不了作業了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天累死人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一場吧  東同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用功讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次考試的目標是…平均分！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是東聰莉  本篇裡也在朝著平均分努力著！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  還沒人接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快一點趕不及啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.66,0:15:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小望！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？快點來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.53,0:15:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家已經到車站了  比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  芽衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄劍道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走  時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓對方等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小望  喂喂？喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣  你今天也出場比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為現在只剩下五個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說了不用你一定要加入啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就拜託你最後再來一次囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的練習賽來我們這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看  之後我們就不再纏你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東同學  前輩們這麼期待  你就再來一次如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須給我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…那個人到底是什麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  要回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個…我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跑來這裡了  就進去看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小東東！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能來太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  有一半給人感覺是威嚇一樣  還是有點那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一般那樣是不會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…小都的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是室江高中劍道部的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是成明高中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天的比賽所以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是突然下雨很是煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我避一下雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  你靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候讓小都看見了會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看！小都快看這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是什麼？野山栗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  要不我們回去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了小都都  身體不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有些不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不去怎麼可以呢  本來人就不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為找了個可愛的孩子來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算我不去也沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  稍微等我一下啦  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是宮崎同學和榮花同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很要好的  總是黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友…女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  其他的部員呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小東東呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.68,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我只是來參觀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是穿上道服才能平靜心靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來一次  防具也一起穿上吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.12,0:19:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼會有這樣的裝備！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很配哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也來擔當裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了  我是成明高中攝影部的小田島禮美  來進行攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那麼請進
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都～笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮美  禮美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳川老師  你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:20:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聽說有練習賽有點在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她參觀沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  請進請進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄙姓石田  今天請林老師多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊才是  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就聽說過您的大名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和老師的學生進行練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說也是個很好的學習機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我們的部員太懶散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我太放縱他們的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個年齡段的孩子都很複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽要開始了  快點帶上頭盔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要出場比賽…這該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣  你是次鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是輸掉比賽  老師又要發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說你為什麼輸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你有什麼地方不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠的地方…根本沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是陪朋友才加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對劍道也沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.37,0:21:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等比賽結束後  我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.28,0:21:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  練習和我一組好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.70,0:22:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:27.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:34.03,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:23:02.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:09.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:17.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:20.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:32.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.33,0:23:35.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:40.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:47.85,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.50,0:23:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是東聰莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.92,0:23:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於在本篇中正式登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我會繼續活躍…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:23:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？已經播放結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.01,0:24:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就不靠集數靠密度來決勝負吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡…眼鏡眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.86,0:24:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下…下集是「東的情況同芽衣的情況」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那是這一話的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:20.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下集  老師們和學生們）
